title: The Roost Southern Kitchen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Counter serve Southern-American soul food in a strip mall. Separate, changing vegetarian menu with a couple of vegan options including pecan patty medallions in gravy and vegan fried fish plus vegan side dishes like mac and cheeze, potato salad, and southern greens.
